membr:Project_Iabdounane rsrch:hasFindings membr:Project_Iabdounane_F250218 .

membr:Project_Iabdounane_F250218 a rsrch:Finding ;
    rdfs:label """The verbal form “this close to V-ing” and the close index finger - thumb gesture co-occur 93% of the time.\r
The two forms are likely entrenched together as a single unit, thus making it one formal multimodal unit.\r
The construction is multimodal.\r
""" ;
    rsrch:basedOn cx:ThisCloseToV-ing .

